profileNotes: The Skiller: Warmonger build focuses on achieving level 99 in all combat skills while keeping non-combat skilling disciplines at a minimum. This build is designed for players who prioritize combat proficiency and aim to master every combat-related aspect of the game. The Warmonger is perfect for PvP, high-level bossing, and Slayer tasks, providing the player with the highest potential for combat efficiency and damage output.
